Title: HW/SW Inventory: Found no data now triggers an OK State
Level: 1
Component: inv
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.2.6p15
Date: 1448461614
Class: fix

In order to simplify the configuration, the HW/SW Inventory check not longer shows a Warning in case of no Data.
Now it's not longer necessary to decide which devices shall get the check and wich not.
